  &lt;h2 id=&quot;btn-groups-nested&quot;&gt;Nesting&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Place a &lt;code&gt;.btn-group&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; within another &lt;code&gt;.btn-group&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; when you want dropdown menus mixed with a series of buttons.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
